#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:2
msgid "lmcache tool"
msgstr "lmcache tool"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:4
msgid ""
"The ``lmcache tool`` command groups offline analysis utilities bundled "
"with LMCache."
msgstr "``lmcache tool`` 命令将与 LMCache 捆绑在一起的离线分析工具进行分组。"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:11
msgid "Currently one tool is available: ``cache-simulator``."
msgstr "目前可用的工具有一个：\\ ``cache-simulator``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:15
msgid ""
"``cache-simulator`` depends on the optional ``plot`` extras "
"(``sortedcontainers`` / ``matplotlib``). If they are not installed, the "
"sub-command is silently omitted from the CLI. Install the extras to "
"enable it."
msgstr "``cache-simulator`` 依赖于可选的 ``plot`` 附加组件（\\ ``sortedcontainers`` / ``matplotlib``\\ ）。如果它们未安装，子命令将会在 CLI 中静默省略。安装附加组件以启用它。"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:22
msgid "cache-simulator"
msgstr "cache-simulator"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:24
msgid ""
"Replay LMCache lookup-hash JSONL logs through an LRU cache to measure the"
" KV-cache token hit rate. It has three actions:"
msgstr "通过 LRU 缓存重放 LMCache 查找哈希 JSONL 日志，以测量 KV Cache 的令牌命中率。它有三个操作："

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:35
msgid "Action"
msgstr "操作"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:36
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:37
msgid "``simulate``"
msgstr "``simulate``"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:38
msgid ""
"Replay logs at a fixed cache capacity; print a text report and save a "
"7-panel statistics PNG."
msgstr "在固定的缓存容量下重放日志；打印文本报告并保存 7 面板的统计 PNG。"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:40
msgid "``sweep``"
msgstr "``sweep``"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:41
msgid ""
"Sweep across a range of cache capacities and save a hit-rate vs. capacity"
" PNG."
msgstr "在一系列缓存容量中进行扫描，并保存命中率与容量的 PNG 图像。"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:43
msgid "``gen-dataset``"
msgstr "``gen-dataset``"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:44
msgid ""
"Generate a ``vllm bench serve`` custom dataset (JSONL) from lookup-hash "
"JSONL logs, preserving prefix-sharing structure."
msgstr "从查找哈希 JSONL 日志生成一个 ``vllm bench serve`` 自定义数据集 (JSONL)，保留前缀共享结构。"

#: ../../source/cli/tool.rst:47
msgid "Each action has its own flags. Run the built-in help for the full list:"
msgstr "每个操作都有其自己的标志。运行内置帮助以获取完整列表："

